## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **abatacept (Orencia) 2024 ATRIUM trial — Cooper et al** = first prospective trial framework for ICI-myocarditis. CTLA-4-Ig T cell co-stimulation block 가 ICI-induced T cell expansion 의 mechanism-targeted 차단. quantum-VQE 의 PPI scaffold 가 직접 fit (CD80/86 interface).
2. **ruxolitinib (Jakafi) JAK1/2 — Cooper 2024 ATRIUM combo** = ICI-myocarditis 응급 STAT 신호 차단. abatacept 와 combo 가 fulminant 응급 mortality 감소. quantum-VQE 의 ATP-competitive pocket fit.
3. **ICI-myocarditis paradigm shift 2021+** = pembrolizumab + nivolumab + ipilimumab + relatlimab combo 후 fulminant myocarditis 사망률 ~50% — corticosteroid alone 부족. cross-cancer cross-immunology.
4. **mRNA vaccine post-2021 청소년 myocarditis** = Pfizer + Moderna 후 16-29세 남성 incidence ~1/10,000-1/50,000. 대부분 self-limited 2-3주 + corticosteroid + NSAID. 만성 진행 rare. cross-vaccinology + adolescent.
5. **COVID-19 + 만성 myocarditis + long COVID** = acute COVID 후 cardiac MRI 잠복 myocarditis evidence. 만성 long COVID + myocarditis overlap. cross-chronic_fatigue + biosecurity_pivot.
6. **giant cell myocarditis** = rare aggressive autoimmune — 사망률 untreated ~90% — combination immunosuppression (ATG + cyclosporine + corticosteroid + alemtuzumab salvage) 필수. cross-emergency_medicine.
7. **eosinophilic myocarditis** = Loeffler endocarditis + Churg-Strauss + drug hypersensitivity (DRESS) — corticosteroid + mepolizumab IL-5 research.
8. **viral myocarditis** = enterovirus (CoxsackieB) + adenovirus + parvovirus B19 + HHV6 + COVID-19. virocapsid axis fit. specific antiviral 부재 — supportive + immunomodulation.
9. **Lyme + Chagas myocarditis** = tropical_ntd cross-link. Chagas 만성 cardiomyopathy DCM 진행 ~30% over decades. 한국 import case rare.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 한정** — quantum-only in-silico, myocarditis 임상 의미 (특히 ICI + giant cell rare disease) 한정. ATRIUM 2024 prospective 외 historical retrospective 다수.

